OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FClear spells
OL,6,Ffor a time this evening, with
OL,7,Ftemperatures quickly falling and
OL,8,Fperhaps a slight frost in places. Then
OL,9,Fcloud increases with showers or longer
OL,10,Fspells of rain arriving from the west,
OL,11,Fmostly clear by dawn. Also becoming
OL,12,Fbreezy.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSunday:FCloudy with outbreaks of rain,
OL,15,Fthese turning light and patchy by late
OL,16,Fmorning. Most places becoming dry and
OL,17,Fperhaps brighter through the
OL,18,Fafternoon. Breezy inland, windy along
OL,19,Fthe coast. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
