OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FBreezy
OL,6,FMonday with rain spreading east but
OL,7,Falso some drier spells. Dry Tuesday
OL,8,Fwith light winds and sunny spells.
OL,9,FCloudy with showers on Wednesday.
OL,10,FTemperatures generally a little above
OL,11,Faverage.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
